Package: libggui-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: ggui-dev
Description: terminal UI library for Meson-based vendoring (development files)
 GGUI is a cross-platform terminal user interface toolkit written in C++17.
 This development package ships the headers, static archive, and tooling
 necessary to vendor GGUI into downstream projects built with Meson.